-- Toronto Mayor Ford Says He’s Not an Addict, Denies Cocaine Use
-- B y   L i e z e l   H i l l
-- 2013-05-24T19:47:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-24/toronto-mayor-ford-says-he-s-not-an-addict-denies-cocaine-use.html
Toronto Mayor Rob Ford says he is not
an addict and denies using  crack cocaine .  “I do not use crack cocaine,” Ford told reporters at city
hall today. “Nor am I an addict of crack cocaine.”  The Toronto Star newspaper said on May 16 two of its
reporters watched a cellphone video allegedly showing Ford
smoking from a crack cocaine pipe. Ford said he can’t comment on
a video he hasn’t seen.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Liezel Hill in Toronto at 
